KY LPhNY HYMYM HHM ShKUr H'aDM L'a NHYH VShKUr HBHMH 'aYNNH VLYVTSh'a VLB'a 'aYN-ShLVM MN-HTShUr V'aShLCh 'aTh-KL-H'aDM 'aYSh BUr'yHV.
V'yThH L'a KYMYM HUr'aShNYM 'aNY LSh'aUrYTh H'yM HZH N'aM YHVH TShB'aVTh.
KY-ZUr'y HShLVM HGPhN ThThN PhUrYH VH'aUrTSh ThThN 'aTh-YBVLH VHShMYM YThNV TLM VHNChLThY 'aTh-Sh'aUrYTh H'yM HZH 'aTh-KL-'aLH.
VHYH K'aShUr HYYThM QLLH BGVYM BYTh YHVDH VBYTh YShUr'aL KN 'aVShY'y 'aThKM VHYYThM BUrKH 'aL-ThYUr'aV ThChZQNH YDYKM.
